{"id":4781,"date":"2023-12-05T14:26:33","date_gmt":"2023-12-05T21:26:33","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.greencentury.com\/?post_type=team&#038;p=4781"},"modified":"2024-06-06T11:07:42","modified_gmt":"2024-06-06T17:07:42","slug":"andrew-shalit","status":"publish","type":"team","link":"https:\/\/www.greencentury.com\/team\/andrew-shalit\/","title":{"rendered":"Andrew Shalit, Shareholder Advocate"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:70%\">\n<p>Andrew Shalit is a Green Century shareholder advocate, leveraging the Funds\u2019 and the firm\u2019s influence as a shareholder to drive companies to adopt more environmentally sustainable policies and practices. Prior to joining Green Century in 2023, he had been an advocate for the environment and society for nearly three decades. He most recently created Steady Type, a touchscreen keyboard for people with hand tremors. In his career, he was also Cofounder of 18by Vote, a non-partisan group working to increase voter turnout by teenagers, Director of Shareholder Advocacy at Green Century Capital Management, and Technology Director at V-Day, the global movement to end violence against women and girls. Andrew has a B.A. in English from Harvard University.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-left:0;flex-basis:30%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"2560\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https:\/\/www.greencentury.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Shalit-Andrew-square-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-21597\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.greencentury.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Shalit-Andrew-square-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/www.greencentury.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Shalit-Andrew-square-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/